version_description:
- NEW: You are now able to rename your ducks!
- NEW: Check your duck's origins by tapping on their parts in the duck reveal screen!
- NEW: Continue to grow your duck collection with the option to gain an extra nest or increase the duck population cap!
- Fixed some fowl bugs that were driving us quackers
- Fixed some fowl bugs that were driving us quackers

- NEW: Duck, duck, frog?!? 90+ new parts to help diversify your flock with even more ducked up combinations
- NEW: A handy list where you can view all the current sacrificesâ€” I mean ducks in your colony!

Disclaimer: No ducks were harmed during the making of this update - apart from those we sacrificed down the hole

- In return for your sacrifices, monsters now leave behind a Cursed egg on their defeat. Hatch these eggs to obtain unique duck heads!
- Birds of a feather flock together - Breed ducks with the right combination of parts to complete the sets prophecized in the Duck Grimoire (formerly known as the Ducktionary)
- Certain ducks are meant for the finer things in life - purchase the Inter-Dimensional Lamp as a place where up to 15 extra ducks can relax and take a break from breeding
- We've also taken care of some bugs that were ruffling our feathers

- As if your flock wasn't weird enough, we've added EVEN MORE duck parts! *quacking intensifies*
- The Grimoire has been expanded with 3 new duck sets. Can you breed the right ducks to fit the bill?
